flowchart TB

A[CREW LOGISTICS]
A --> B[HOTEL]
A --> RF[REIMBURSEMENT / FEEDBACK]

%% HOTEL MENU
B --> QC[QUERY / CONCERN]
B --> PP[POLICY & PROCEDURES]
B --> RF

%% QUERY / CONCERN BRANCHES
QC --> HCN[Hotel Cab Not Received]
QC --> IHN[Issue / Need Assistance in Hotel]
QC --> HCI[Hotel Cab Clubbing Issue]
QC --> HSE[Hotel Stay Extension]
QC --> DUH[Day Use Hotel]
QC --> RELO[Relocation]

%% HOTEL CAB NOT RECEIVED
HCN --> AH[Airport to Hotel]
HCN --> HA[Hotel to Airport / Training]

AH --> AHQ["Asked: Contacted hotel?"]
AHQ --> AHY[YES → Crew types outcome → Transfer to Agent]
AHQ --> AHN[NO → Advise to call hotel → Transfer to Agent]

HA --> HAA[If Airport → Transfer to Agent]
HA --> HAT[If Training → Create Ticket]
HAT --> HAT2["Reporting <2 hrs? → Transfer to Agent"]

%% ISSUE / NEED ASSISTANCE
IHN --> I1[Hygiene / Service / Noise]
IHN --> I2[Waiting for Room]
IHN --> I3[Twin / King Bed Issue]
IHN --> I4[Laundry Issue]
IHN --> I5[Hotel Staff Behaviour]
IHN --> I6[Meals Concern]
IHN --> I7[Incident / Safety Concern]
IHN --> I8[Any Other → Crew Types]

I1 --> TA1[Transfer to Agent]
I2 --> TA1
I3 --> TA1
I4 --> TA1
I5 --> TA1
I6 --> TA1
I7 --> TA1
I8 --> TA1

%% HOTEL CAB CLUBBING
HCI --> TCB[Transfer to Agent]

%% STAY EXTENSION
HSE --> SE1[Request Acknowledged]
HSE --> SE2["Cabin Relocation? → Needs IFS Approval"]
SE2 --> SE3[Email crew.logistics@goindigo.in]
HSE --> SE4[Create Ticket]

%% DAY USE HOTEL
DUH --> DH1[Check Halt Duration]
DH1 --> DH2[Halt < 4 hrs]
DH1 --> DH3[Halt ≥ 4 hrs]

DH2 --> DH2A[No Hotel Found → Not Authorized]
DH2 --> DH2B[Hotel Found → Show Options]

DH3 --> DH3A[Operating Crew → Hotel Info in Crew App]
DH3 --> DH3B[Training Cockpit → Hotel Info in Crew App]
DH3 --> DH3C[Training Cabin → Day Use Not Authorized]

%% RELOCATION
RELO --> R1[Needs IFS Base Head Approval]

%% REIMBURSEMENT / FEEDBACK
RF --> RFM[Reimbursement → Create Ticket → Transfer]
RF --> FB1[Cockpit → URL Form → Close]
RF --> FB2[Cabin → Create Ticket → Close]
